    - "INTENTIONAL MEDIUM": Clear evidence of a specific tool being used (e.g., digital brush strokes with varying opacity, oil paint impasto, charcoal grain, vector-perfect geometric precision).
    - "LOGICAL LIGHTING": Shadows and highlights that follow a single, coherent light source across the entire scene.
    - "STORYTELLING": Details that aren't just "there" for complexity, but serve a narrative purpose.
    - "CONSISTENT TEXEL DENSITY": Textures that maintain logical scale and sharpness relative to their distance from the camera.

    SCORING PROTOCOL:
    - 1.0 - 3.0: Obvious AI Slop. Instant failure.
    - 3.1 - 5.0: Sophisticated AI with major logic errors.
    - 5.1 - 7.0: High-effort AI or mediocre human work. Be suspicious.
    - 7.1 - 8.9: Skilled Human Artistry or exceptionally well-prompted/edited AI. Look for the "soul".
    - 9.0 - 10.0: Master-tier professional design. Flawless execution.

    Use decimal precision (e.g., 2.3, 8.7, 9.1). NEVER give a generic 8.0 if you see even one "slop" artifact. Be a harsh critic.
  `;

  const base64Data = base64Image.includes(',') ? base64Image.split(',')[1] : base64Image;

  const response = await ai.models.generateContent({
    model,
    contents: {
      parts: [
        {
          inlineData: {
            mimeType,
            data: base64Data,
          },
        },
        {
          text: "Perform a ruthless forensic audit. Detect the slop. Is this a human masterpiece or synthetic garbage? Provide a decimal score and forensic report in JSON."
        },
      ],
    },
    config: {
      systemInstruction,
      responseMimeType: "application/json",
      responseSchema: {
        type: Type.OBJECT,
        properties: {
          score: { type: Type.NUMBER, description: "Unforgiving rating from 1.0-10.0" },
          isAiGenerated: { type: Type.BOOLEAN, description: "True if any synthetic indicators are found" },
          confidence: { type: Type.NUMBER, description: "Forensic certainty percentage" },
          reasoning: { type: Type.STRING, description: "Brutally honest explanation of the score" },
          technicalDetails: { 
            type: Type.ARRAY, 
            items: { type: Type.STRING },
            description: "Evidence found (e.g., 'warped brush patterns', 'coherent global illumination')"
          },
        },
        required: ["score", "isAiGenerated", "confidence", "reasoning", "technicalDetails"],
      },
    },
  });

  const jsonStr = response.text?.trim() || "{}";
  return JSON.parse(jsonStr) as GeminiResponse;
};

